{"tid":1204963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"若中共血腥鎮壓香港，美國會出兵阻止嗎？","createTime":"2019-06-11T16:37:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T11:27:31.000Z","uid":177168,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"e71a28cd683ea2c5607c342cf247d8e2bf0ee8c6","tid":1204963,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T16:37:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://disp.cc/b/163-brYb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdisp.cc%2Fb%2F163-brYb&d=TV1mljVccv2Dt1EdWC3TieQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=db57080a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://disp.cc/b/163-brYb</a><br />\n<br />\n如題，大家認為川普會救港人嗎？<br />\n<br />\n話說，雖然香港跟中國已經是一個國家了，但允許兩制存在的情況下，港人血液中還是存<br />\n在追求自由的基因！不要說不可能，中共或許就在等這個時機好好準備大清洗！ <br />\n<br />\n但國際社會能容許這種事發生嗎？<br />\n<br />\n身為堅守自由主義並希望中國走向自由民主的美國老大哥，更沒有理由眼睜睜看著香港被<br />\n胡搞瞎搞吧？ <br />\n<br />\n想分別聽聽：<br />\n(1) 港人有何期待？<br />\n(2) 台灣人有何想法？<br />\n(3) 若香港被血腥鎮壓，台灣人能如何協助港人？"},{"pid":"4004f8c05839fd72a6a989b35a55aeb1543ece57","tid":1204963,"uid":249885,"like":63,"dislike":2,"score":61,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T16:38:56.000Z","msg":"不會"},{"pid":"49b597d633443d6a8fbb467956d73fce433242f9","tid":1204963,"uid":218626,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T16:44:38.000Z","msg":"Nope"},{"pid":"22a6fa4f78f39a6157f9ce125681afabb59127a5","tid":1204963,"uid":93784,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T16:45:39.000Z","msg":"跳哂Step <br />\n<br />\n應該係香港人會出黎反擊嗎?"},{"pid":"c1c6c4b66905c65754b3d55110973eda6e3fecb2","tid":1204963,"uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T16:46:34.000Z","msg":"我覺得會大動作阻止 唔一定係出兵<br />\n<br />\n但反而血腥鎮壓機會仲細"},{"pid":"f66956c28306c3b4fb0a6357db06ca011804ad42","tid":1204963,"uid":103230,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T16:46:43.000Z","msg":"唔會<br />\n但係佢會制裁大陸"},{"pid":"70ddf08dc11f0d5727fd9d9652ef377b543a34e4","tid":1204963,"uid":140802,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score"